        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  children and adolescents (6-16 years);

          -  obese (OB) and normal weight (NW, control group) according to the International
             Obesity Task Force (IOTF) criteria;

          -  both genders;

          -  diet naÃ¯ve.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  specific causes of endocrine or genetic obesity;

          -  type 1 or type 2 diabetes;

